Colour. Pale yellow to dark brown (
Martin et al. 2016
).

Size. Ovig. females 15–30 mm ; males 6–15 mm (
Martin et al. 2016
).

Distribution. Reliable records are entirely from Pacific and Indian Ocean: Bangkok , Thailand ( Schiöedte & Meinert 1884 ), Beirut ( Trilles & Bariche 2006 ), India ( Chilton 1924 ; Veerapan & Ravichandran 2000 ;
Rajkumar et al. 2004
, 2005a , 2005b ; Ravi & Rajkumar 2007 ; Trilles & Bariche 2006 ; Trilles et al. 2011), Australia ( Hale 1926 ; McNeill 1926 ;
Jones et al. 2008
;
Martin et al. 2016
), Indonesia ( Nierstrasz 1931 ; Trilles 2008 ) and Vietnam (Trilles 1975).
